Best Fit

DFArunsbest <- rbind((DFAruns15S %>% mutate(Year= "SI2015") %>% filter(AICc== min(AICc))), 
                    (DFAruns16S %>% mutate(Year= "SI2016")%>% filter(AICc== min(AICc))),
                    (DFAruns18S %>% mutate(Year= "SI2018")%>% filter(AICc== min(AICc))),
                    (DFAruns15M %>% mutate(Year= "MC2015")%>% filter(AICc== min(AICc))),
                    (DFAruns16M %>% mutate(Year= "MC2016")%>% filter(AICc== min(AICc))),
                    (DFAruns17M %>% mutate(Year= "MC2017")%>% filter(AICc== min(AICc))),
                    (DFAruns18M %>% mutate(Year= "MC2018")%>% filter(AICc== min(AICc))))
DFArunsbest <- DFArunsbest %>% select(Year, AICc, m, R, Covariate)
